This project requires to have preinstalled:
    Node
    NPM

Install libraries with:
    npm Install

Launch tests with:
    npm test


To see report on windows, look for "chrome.bat" in Allure report folder and double click it

To see report on mac, ensure Chrome is closed, and execute this command in a terminal (if Chrome is already opened, the command wont do anything):

	open /Applications/Google\ Chrome.app --args --allow-file-access-from-files

	This will open a Chrome app with permissions to open the report.
	Then just open the index.html file